freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Swelling and severe pain in hand wrist and elbows. Also numbness and tingling followed by severe pain in right hand that goes away. Slight discomfort like that in left hand. Achy all over.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Achy normally but much more so today. Also have had numbness off and on right hand which is new since shot. On opposite arm of shot
Less pain, numbness, and tingling in  right hand
More achy than usual, still have tingling in my right hand off and on
